    <string name="remote_usb_tether_guide_step_4">When db link asks for permission to access the camera, tap Yes.</string>
    <string name="remote_usb_tether_guide_note_primary">Current USB tethering supports wired live view, saving captured files to the camera and phone, and basic controls only.</string>
    <string name="remote_usb_tether_guide_note_secondary">Some detailed features may not work. If you want to check more detailed functions, connect the camera in tethering mode and swipe from left to right to open the side menu.</string>
